abstracts.cdata!:
The Highway Maintenance Project Loan for
            Equatorial Guinea was approved by the Board in March 1973.
            On July 2, 1975, it was decided at a Loan Committee Meeting,
            and following consultation with United Nations Development
            Program (UNDP), to cancel the credit. Formal cancellation of
            the total Credit took place on April 13, 1976.
